high_descs: Turn around and step towards the counter then take a step to your left and walk to the soap dispenser on the counter to your right and turn right to face it when you get there.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of you.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter then turn right to face the toaster.
Put the tomato under the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the White table in the middle of the kitchen.
Pick up the tomato on the white table between the two heads of lettuce.
Walk around the white table to the microwave next to the refrigerator.
Microwave the tomato for a moment, then take it back out and shut the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the toaster on the counter above the dishwasher.
Put the heated tomato on the counter next to the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a tomato and set it next to the toaster.

high_descs: Walk over to the side of the kitchen island behind you.
Pick up the tomato off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn right and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave up and take out the now heated tomato then close the microwave.
Turn around and walk over to where the toaster is on the counter.
Put the heated tomato on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the counter.
